{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":481,"text":"As a matter of fact,"},{"time":2015,"text":"I was trying to think about my career\nsince I left the White House,"},{"time":5287,"text":"and the best example I have is a cartoon\nin The New Yorker a couple of years ago."},{"time":9583,"text":"This little boy is looking up\nat his father,"},{"time":11742,"text":"and he says, \"Daddy, when I grow up,\nI want to be a former president.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":15787,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":17477,"text":"Well, I have had a great blessing\nas a former president,"},{"time":21193,"text":"because I have had an access"},{"time":23620,"text":"that very few other people\nin the world have ever had"},{"time":26277,"text":"to get to know so many people\naround this whole universe."},{"time":29923,"text":"Not only am I familiar\nwith the 50 states in the United States,"},{"time":33545,"text":"but also my wife and I have visited\nmore than 145 countries in the world,"},{"time":38421,"text":"and the Carter Center has had full-time\nprograms in 80 nations on Earth."},{"time":42670,"text":"And a lot of times,\nwhen we go into a country,"},{"time":44866,"text":"we not only the meet\nthe king or the president,"},{"time":47076,"text":"but we also meet the villagers who live\nin the most remote areas of Africa."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51424,"text":"So our overall commitment\nat the Carter Center"},{"time":54930,"text":"is to promote human rights,"},{"time":56927,"text":"and knowing the world as I do,\nI can tell you without any equivocation"},{"time":61639,"text":"that the number one abuse\nof human rights on Earth"},{"time":65530,"text":"is, strangely, not addressed quite often,\nis the abuse of women and girls."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71369,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":74657,"text":"There are a couple of reasons for this\nthat I'll mention to begin with."},{"time":79890,"text":"First of all is the misinterpretation\nof religious scriptures, holy scriptures,"},{"time":85360,"text":"in the Bible, Old Testament,\nNew Testament, Quran and so forth,"},{"time":88983,"text":"and these have been misinterpreted by men\nwho are now in the ascendant positions"},{"time":96246,"text":"in the synagogues and the churches\nand in the mosques."},{"time":98875,"text":"And they interpret these rules\nto make sure that women"},{"time":102706,"text":"are ordinarily relegated\nto a secondary position"},{"time":106960,"text":"compared to men in the eyes of God."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110558,"text":"This is a very serious problem.\nIt's ordinarily not addressed."},{"time":114780,"text":"A number of years ago, in the year 2000,"},{"time":116891,"text":"I had been a Baptist,\na Southern Baptist for 70 years --"},{"time":120454,"text":"I tell you, I still teach\nSunday school every Sunday;"},{"time":122936,"text":"I'll be teaching this Sunday as well --"},{"time":124807,"text":"but the Southern Baptist Convention\nin the year 2000 decided"},{"time":129222,"text":"that women should play\na secondary position,"},{"time":131823,"text":"a subservient position to men."},{"time":133889,"text":"So they issued an edict, in effect,"},{"time":136606,"text":"that prevents women from being priests,\npastors, deacons in the church,"},{"time":142510,"text":"or chaplains in the military,"},{"time":144802,"text":"and if a woman teaches a classroom"},{"time":147960,"text":"in a Southern Baptist seminary,"},{"time":150142,"text":"they cannot teach if a boy is in the room,"},{"time":153555,"text":"because you can find verses in the Bible,"},{"time":155576,"text":"there's over 30,000 verses in the Bible,"},{"time":158600,"text":"that say that a woman shouldn't\nteach a man, and so forth."},{"time":161410,"text":"But the basic thing is the scriptures\nare misinterpreted"},{"time":164445,"text":"to keep men in an ascendant position."},{"time":166906,"text":"That is an all-pervasive problem,"},{"time":168996,"text":"because men can exert that power"},{"time":173872,"text":"and if an abusive husband or an employer,\nfor instance, wants to cheat women,"},{"time":179886,"text":"they can say that if women\nare not equal in the eyes of God,"},{"time":183670,"text":"why should I treat them as equals myself?"},{"time":185862,"text":"Why should I pay them equal pay\nfor doing the same kind of work?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":190320,"text":"The other very serious blight"},{"time":192247,"text":"that causes this problem\nis the excessive resort to violence,"},{"time":196264,"text":"and that is increasing\ntremendously around the world."},{"time":200858,"text":"In the United States of America,\nfor instance, we have had"},{"time":203787,"text":"an enormous increase\nin abuse of poor people,"},{"time":207967,"text":"mostly black people and minorities,\nby putting them in prison."},{"time":213261,"text":"When I was in office\nas governor of Georgia,"},{"time":215815,"text":"one out of every 1,000 Americans\nwere in prison."},{"time":219181,"text":"Nowadays, 7.3 people\nper 1,000 are in prison."},{"time":224290,"text":"That's a sevenfold increase."},{"time":226310,"text":"And since I left the White House,"},{"time":227958,"text":"there's been an 800 percent increase\nin the number of women"},{"time":231279,"text":"who are black who are in prison."},{"time":233856,"text":"We also have\n[one of the only countries] on Earth"},{"time":236380,"text":"that still has the death penalty\nthat is a developed country."},{"time":240334,"text":"And we rank right alongside\nthe countries that are most abusive"},{"time":243701,"text":"in all elements of human rights\nin encouraging the death penalty."},{"time":247555,"text":"We're in California now,\nand I figured out the other day"},{"time":250411,"text":"that California has spent\nfour billion dollars"},{"time":253406,"text":"in convicting 13 people\nfor the death penalty."},{"time":257818,"text":"If you add that up, that's 307 million\ndollars it costs California"},{"time":262653,"text":"to send a person to be executed."},{"time":265991,"text":"Nebraska this week just passed a law\nabolishing the death penalty,"},{"time":269474,"text":"because it costs so much. (Applause)"},{"time":274861,"text":"So the resort to violence and abuse\nof poor people and helpless people"},{"time":279087,"text":"is another cause of the increase\nin abuse of women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":283475,"text":"Let me just go down a very few\nabuses of women that concern me most,"},{"time":287979,"text":"and I'll be fairly brief, because I have\na limited amount of time, as you know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291880,"text":"One is genital mutilation."},{"time":296360,"text":"Genital mutilation is horrible\nand not known by American women,"},{"time":300474,"text":"but in some countries, many countries,"},{"time":304219,"text":"when a child is born that's a girl,\nvery soon in her life,"},{"time":308525,"text":"her genitals are completely cut away\nby a so-called cutter"},{"time":315235,"text":"who has a razor blade and,\nin a non-sterilized way,"},{"time":319227,"text":"they remove the exterior parts\nof a woman's genitalia."},{"time":323170,"text":"And sometimes, in more extreme cases\nbut not very rare cases,"},{"time":327591,"text":"they sew the orifice up so the girl\ncan just urinate or menstruate."},{"time":331405,"text":"And then later, when she gets married,\nthe same cutter goes in"},{"time":334784,"text":"and opens the orifice up\nso she can have sex."},{"time":337400,"text":"This is not a rare thing, although\nit's against the law in most countries."},{"time":341415,"text":"In Egypt, for instance,"},{"time":343347,"text":"91 percent of all the females\nthat live in Egypt today"},{"time":347000,"text":"have been sexually mutilated in that way."},{"time":349560,"text":"In some countries,\nit's more than 98 percent"},{"time":352950,"text":"of the women are cut that way\nbefore they reach maturity."},{"time":357246,"text":"This is a horrible affliction"},{"time":359846,"text":"on all women that live in those countries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":363515,"text":"Another very serious thing\nis honor killings,"},{"time":367299,"text":"where a family with misinterpretation,\nagain, of a holy scripture --"},{"time":370625,"text":"there's nothing in the Quran\nthat mandates this --"},{"time":373313,"text":"will execute a girl in their family"},{"time":377500,"text":"if she is raped"},{"time":379377,"text":"or if she marries a man\nthat her father does not approve,"},{"time":383112,"text":"or sometimes even if she\nwears inappropriate clothing."},{"time":386223,"text":"And this is done by members\nof her own family,"},{"time":389251,"text":"so the family becomes murderers"},{"time":391456,"text":"when the girl brings\nso-called disgrace to the family."},{"time":395808,"text":"An analysis was done in Egypt\nnot so long ago by the United Nations"},{"time":399155,"text":"and it showed that 75 percent\nof these murders of a girl"},{"time":403197,"text":"are perpetrated by the father,\nthe uncle or the brother,"},{"time":408580,"text":"but 25 percent of the murders\nare conducted by women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":412032,"text":"Another problem that we have in the world"},{"time":413994,"text":"that relates to women\nparticularly is slavery,"},{"time":416732,"text":"or human trafficking it's called nowadays."},{"time":419147,"text":"There were about 12.5 million people\nsold from Africa into slavery"},{"time":423565,"text":"in the New World back in\nthe 19th century and the 18th century."},{"time":427784,"text":"There are 30 million people\nnow living in slavery."},{"time":431639,"text":"The United States Department of State\nnow has a mandate from Congress"},{"time":437281,"text":"to give a report every year,"},{"time":439603,"text":"and the State Department reports\nthat 800,000 people are sold"},{"time":444246,"text":"across international borders\nevery year into slavery,"},{"time":447893,"text":"and that 80 percent\nof those sold are women,"},{"time":450841,"text":"into sexual slavery."},{"time":452977,"text":"In the United States right this moment,"},{"time":455531,"text":"60,000 people are living\nin human bondage, or slavery."},{"time":459385,"text":"Atlanta, Georgia, where\nthe Carter Center is located"},{"time":462171,"text":"and where I teach at Emory University,"},{"time":464772,"text":"they have between 200 and 300 women,\npeople sold into slavery every month."},{"time":470672,"text":"It's the number one place\nin the nation because of that."},{"time":473781,"text":"Atlanta has the busiest\nairport in the world,"},{"time":475987,"text":"and they also have a lot of passengers\nthat come from the Southern Hemisphere."},{"time":481234,"text":"If a brothel owner"},{"time":483858,"text":"wants to buy a girl\nthat has brown or black skin,"},{"time":486877,"text":"they can do it for 1,000 dollars."},{"time":489523,"text":"A white-skinned girl brings\nseveral times more than that,"},{"time":493610,"text":"and the average brothel owner in Atlanta\nand in the United States now"},{"time":497000,"text":"can earn about $35,000 per slave."},{"time":501504,"text":"The sex trade in Atlanta, Georgia, exceeds\nthe total drug trade in Atlanta, Georgia."},{"time":506613,"text":"So this is another very serious problem,\nand the basic problem is prostitution,"},{"time":511465,"text":"because there's not\na whorehouse in America"},{"time":515459,"text":"that's not known by the local officials,"},{"time":517688,"text":"the local policemen, or the chief\nof police or the mayor and so forth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":521659,"text":"And this leads to one\nof the worst problems,"},{"time":524386,"text":"and that is that women are bought\nincreasingly and put into sexual slavery"},{"time":528635,"text":"in all countries in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530586,"text":"Sweden has got a good approach to it."},{"time":533140,"text":"About 15 to 20 years ago, Sweden\ndecided to change the law,"},{"time":536762,"text":"and women are no longer prosecuted"},{"time":539316,"text":"if they are in sexual slavery,"},{"time":542100,"text":"but the brothel owners and the pimps\nand the male customers are prosecuted,"},{"time":547675,"text":"and -- (Applause) --\nprostitution has gone down."},{"time":552463,"text":"In the United States, we take\njust the opposite position."},{"time":555477,"text":"For every male arrested\nfor illegal sex trade,"},{"time":561664,"text":"25 women are arrested\nin the United States of America."},{"time":567120,"text":"Canada, Ireland, I've already said Sweden,"},{"time":571230,"text":"France, and other countries are moving now\ntowards this so-called Swedish model."},{"time":575150,"text":"That's another thing that can be done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577309,"text":"We have two great institutions\nin this country that all of us admire:"},{"time":580680,"text":"our military and our great\nuniversity system."},{"time":584511,"text":"In the military, they are now analyzing\nhow many sexual assaults take place."},{"time":588830,"text":"The last report I got,\nthere were 26,000 sexual assaults"},{"time":593219,"text":"that took place in the military --"},{"time":595564,"text":"26,000."},{"time":597210,"text":"Only 3,000, not much more than 1 percent,\nare actually prosecuted,"},{"time":602420,"text":"and the reason is that the commanding\nofficer of any organization --"},{"time":606590,"text":"a ship like my submarine,\nor a battalion in the Army"},{"time":610842,"text":"or a company in the Marines --"},{"time":612978,"text":"the commanding officer\nhas the right under law to decide"},{"time":617103,"text":"whether to prosecute a rapist or not,"},{"time":619688,"text":"and of course, the last thing they want\nis for anybody to know"},{"time":622869,"text":"that under their command,\nsexual assaults are taking place,"},{"time":626306,"text":"so they do not do it."},{"time":628210,"text":"That law needs to be changed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":631472,"text":"About one out of four girls\nwho enter American universities"},{"time":634664,"text":"will be sexually assaulted\nbefore she graduates,"},{"time":637451,"text":"and this is now getting\na lot of publicity,"},{"time":639737,"text":"partially because of my book,\nbut other things,"},{"time":641943,"text":"and so 89 universities in America\nare now condemned"},{"time":646131,"text":"by the Department of Education\nunder Title IX"},{"time":648816,"text":"because the officials of the universities\nare not taking care of the women"},{"time":653529,"text":"to protect them from sexual assault."},{"time":655480,"text":"The Department of Justice says\nthat more than half of the rapes"},{"time":659148,"text":"on a college campus\ntake place by serial rapists,"},{"time":662631,"text":"because outside of the university system,"},{"time":665209,"text":"if they rape somebody,\nthey'll be prosecuted,"},{"time":668227,"text":"but when they get on a university campus,\nthey can rape with impunity."},{"time":672255,"text":"They're not prosecuted."},{"time":674298,"text":"Those are the kinds of things\nthat go on in our society."}]},{"cues":[{"time":677642,"text":"Another thing that's very serious\nabout the abuse of women and girls"},{"time":683214,"text":"is the lack of equal pay for equal work,"},{"time":688207,"text":"as you know. (Applause)"},{"time":690296,"text":"And this is sometimes misinterpreted,\nbut for full-time employment,"},{"time":697133,"text":"a woman in the United States now\ngets 23 percent less than a man."},{"time":700480,"text":"When I became president,\nthe difference was 39 percent."},{"time":703369,"text":"So we've made some progress,\npartially because I was president"},{"time":707246,"text":"and so forth -- (Applause) (Laughter) --"},{"time":713160,"text":"but in the last 15 years,\nthere's been no progress made,"},{"time":716568,"text":"so it's been just about 23\nor 24 percent difference"},{"time":719424,"text":"for the last 15 years."},{"time":721699,"text":"These are the kind of things that go on."},{"time":723627,"text":"If you take the Fortune 500 companies,"},{"time":726710,"text":"23 of them have women CEOs,"},{"time":729849,"text":"out of 500,"},{"time":731660,"text":"and those CEOs, I need not tell you,"},{"time":734795,"text":"make less on an average"},{"time":736792,"text":"than the other CEOs."},{"time":739910,"text":"Well, that's what goes on in our country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":742388,"text":"Another problem with the United States"},{"time":744872,"text":"is we are the most warlike\nnation on Earth."},{"time":748564,"text":"We have been to war\nwith about 25 different countries"},{"time":752790,"text":"since the Second World War."},{"time":755251,"text":"Sometimes, we've had soldiers\non the ground fighting."},{"time":757782,"text":"The other times,\nwe've been flying overhead"},{"time":759802,"text":"dropping bombs on people."},{"time":761775,"text":"Other times, of course, now, we have\ndrones that attack people and so forth."},{"time":765537,"text":"We've been at war\nwith 25 different countries"},{"time":768210,"text":"or more since the Second World War."},{"time":770993,"text":"There was four years,\nI won't say which ones,"},{"time":773370,"text":"where we didn't --"},{"time":774964,"text":"(Applause) -- we didn't drop a bomb,\nwe didn't launch a missile,"},{"time":780722,"text":"we didn't fire a bullet."},{"time":782464,"text":"But anyway, those kinds of things,\nthe resort to violence"},{"time":786860,"text":"and the misinterpretation\nof the holy scriptures"},{"time":789476,"text":"are what causes, are the basic causes,\nof abuse of women and girls."}]},{"cues":[{"time":794770,"text":"There's one more basic cause\nthat I need not mention,"},{"time":798369,"text":"and that is that in general,\nmen don't give a damn."},{"time":803710,"text":"(Applause)\nThat's true."},{"time":806751,"text":"The average man that might say,\nI'm against the abuse of women and girls"},{"time":811777,"text":"quietly accepts the privileged\nposition that we occupy,"},{"time":816130,"text":"and this is very similar\nto what I knew when I was a child,"},{"time":819570,"text":"when separate but equal had existed."},{"time":821797,"text":"Racial discrimination, legally,\nhad existed for 100 years,"},{"time":827440,"text":"from 1865 at the end of the War\nBetween the States, the Civil War,"},{"time":830573,"text":"all the way up to the 1960s,"},{"time":833417,"text":"when Lyndon Johnson got the bills passed"},{"time":836134,"text":"for equal rights."},{"time":838107,"text":"But during that time,\nthere were many white people"},{"time":840847,"text":"that didn't think that\nracial discrimination was okay,"},{"time":844214,"text":"but they stayed quiet,"},{"time":846373,"text":"because they enjoyed the privileges\nof better jobs,"},{"time":851507,"text":"unique access to jury duty,"},{"time":854918,"text":"better schools, and everything else,"},{"time":857169,"text":"and that's the same thing\nthat exists today,"},{"time":859330,"text":"because the average man\nreally doesn't care."},{"time":862975,"text":"Even though they say, \"I'm against\ndiscrimination against girls and women,\""},{"time":869320,"text":"they enjoy a privileged position."},{"time":872770,"text":"And it's very difficult to get\nthe majority of men"},{"time":875142,"text":"who control the university system,"},{"time":878188,"text":"the majority of men that control\nthe military system,"},{"time":880852,"text":"the majority of men that control\nthe governments of the world,"},{"time":884350,"text":"and the majority of men that control\nthe great religions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":889584,"text":"So what is the basic thing\nthat we need to do today?"},{"time":892997,"text":"I would say the best thing\nthat we could do today"},{"time":895528,"text":"is for the women in the powerful nations"},{"time":899840,"text":"like this one, and where you come from,"},{"time":902563,"text":"Europe and so forth, who have influence\nand who have freedom to speak and to act,"},{"time":907532,"text":"need to take the responsibility\non yourselves"},{"time":912558,"text":"to be more forceful in demanding"},{"time":915623,"text":"an end to racial discrimination\nagainst girls and women"},{"time":920265,"text":"all over the world."},{"time":921626,"text":"The average woman in Egypt"},{"time":924527,"text":"doesn't have much to say\nabout her daughters"},{"time":926693,"text":"getting genitally mutilated and so forth."},{"time":930101,"text":"I didn't even go down\nto detail about that."},{"time":932175,"text":"But I hope that out of this conference,"},{"time":934234,"text":"that every woman here \nwill get your husbands to realize"},{"time":938748,"text":"that these abuses on the college campuses\nand the military and so forth"},{"time":942872,"text":"and in the future job market,"},{"time":945411,"text":"need to protect your daughters\nand your granddaughters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":949860,"text":"I have 12 grandchildren,\nfour children, and 10 great-grandchildren,"},{"time":955622,"text":"and I think often about them"},{"time":957546,"text":"and about the plight that they\nwill face in America,"},{"time":960611,"text":"not only if they lived in Egypt\nor a foreign country,"},{"time":964396,"text":"in having equal rights,"},{"time":966602,"text":"and I hope that all of you will join me"},{"time":968935,"text":"in being a champion for women\nand girls around the world\n"},{"time":972662,"text":"and protect their human rights."},{"time":974217,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":977189,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}